{"tid":950126,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(朋友) 被指違反簽證規定   印度一次趕走59名中國專家","createTime":"2018-12-21T09:38:12.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-22T03:15:51.000Z","uid":184679,"like":27,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"41b040ed4f4efec030fa804f7c78056991515e65","tid":950126,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-21T09:38:12.000Z","msg":"印度官方機構「外國人註冊辦公室」（FRRO）近日發出逐客令，要求持商業簽證的59名中國專業人士離開印度。接待這批中國專家的印度公司不服命令，決定向法院申訴。<br />\n<br />\n綜合印媒報導，FRRO在本月15日以違反商業簽證為由，要求59名中國專業人士離境。接待的孟買手機製造商「太平洋網路科技」批評，FRRO的命令極端、專制武斷且不公不義，此舉已危害到了公司與外國技術人員交流合作的權利，強調專家們在訪問期間增進了勞動力的專業知識與技能，這些權利是過去2年來必要的產業需求，<br />\n<br />\n太平洋網路科技辯護律師指出，公司致力配合政府「印度製造」的計畫，這些專業人士的貢獻有助於國家利益。報導中提到，太平洋網路科技的辦公室註冊在孟買，工廠位在達曼及錫爾瓦薩，股東大部分在香港，過去7個月來已製造550萬隻手機。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2649135\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2649135&d=3OQGOEmz9Ym3FKyzYyZMx5UWI6eGpREPWAa3TRi9Bo4%3D&h=98d86c54\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2649135&h=53645985\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2649135</a>"},{"pid":"ce4b4aa1ef105083bcaebd9b747c990b28311e99","tid":950126,"uid":74908,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-21T09:44:00.000Z","msg":"繼續keep住佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"efb9cf4a3b535918be78fb3b2d1263858c8ffdb9","tid":950126,"uid":184679,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-21T09:44:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/gBcYNchjBnY/hqdefault.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.ytimg.com%2Fvi%2FgBcYNchjBnY%2Fhqdefault.jpg&h=6ef71c47&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8257df28539af8b43d63e77fb96f86bccd568f1a","tid":950126,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"efb9cf4a3b535918be78fb3b2d1263858c8ffdb9","tid":950126